  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hostile Lands is a 2D top-down roguelite shooter where a crash landing is mistaken for an act of war. The game moves through 7 environments, where players will encounter many types of enemies, find many unique weapons and discover the reason behind the crash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With procedurally generated levels, alternate bosses, and random gun spawns, players will have a unique experience every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/b856b929fccbbceccbead196028ea325.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/03598419bcf9ff7f03f778571264d008.poster.avif?t=1747926077\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/03598419bcf9ff7f03f778571264d008.webm?t=1747926077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/03598419bcf9ff7f03f778571264d008.mp4?t=1747926077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Collect them All!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 different gun types for all play styles: Pistols, Revolvers, Shotguns, SMGs, Assault Rifles, Sniper Rifles, Crossbows, Bladeguns…and perhaps some secrets you’ll just have to discover for yourself…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/4c4c74bd5e6ad34fdc5b7ae9a4e2a8b2.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/0d6c2261367e9f67f6102ae6767dd8b8.avif?t=1747926077\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras_big/0d6c2261367e9f67f6102ae6767dd8b8.avif?t=1747926077 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Play your way!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has a unique skill that you can use once per level. So whether you want to decimate your enemies with Robert’s Blazing Barrels or turn them against each other with Maria’s Psych Strike, you’ll hold your own in the Hostile Lands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plus every character has a passive buff so if you want a little extra speed to dodge bullets or some extra health to absorb them, we got you covered! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/85152f59a2af6f7fa67e80ddf96ddd30.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/0c3c1f27d3813bde4156326e31e0eaab.poster.avif?t=1747926077\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/0c3c1f27d3813bde4156326e31e0eaab.webm?t=1747926077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Some Hostile Variety!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each with its own theme, enemies, bosses and loot will guarantee a new experience every run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/c55b6138c63fb4fdcc43f6772b0ae332.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/d9fdf6cc3ce1fa36405df2776b9e5b3a.avif?t=1747926077\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras_big/d9fdf6cc3ce1fa36405df2776b9e5b3a.avif?t=1747926077 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Feel the Power!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run you’ll gain “Tech” points which can be used to purchases upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our permanent progression system means you get to keep your hard won achievements…even when starting a new run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/55bec765b8e3bb7a00e0154d7718f4ce.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/c961c9cb56280226f87f8b6864510f93.avif?t=1747926077\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras_big/c961c9cb56280226f87f8b6864510f93.avif?t=1747926077 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Lots of Options!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal - when you’re just starting out. Try, fail, buy some upgrades, dominate your foes and prepare for the mayhem of Hard Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard Mode - when you need a challenge. More enemies, more bullets, more guns!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival - how long can you last against continuous waves of vicious enemies howling for your blood?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/19675302db0d87b9d39d7540df52ff0f.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hostile Lands is currently in Early Access.  This means that YOU have a chance to shape the future of the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have lots of ideas to make Hostile Lands a memorable experience…but we can’t do it without you! If you have any suggestions or need to report a bug, please leave a comment in our discussion boards.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’ll do our best to make this the best game possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hostile Lands is a 2D top-down roguelite shooter where a crash landing is mistaken for an act of war. The game moves through 7 environments, where players will encounter many types of enemies, find many unique weapons and discover the reason behind the crash.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With procedurally generated levels, alternate bosses, and random gun spawns, players will have a unique experience every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/b856b929fccbbceccbead196028ea325.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/03598419bcf9ff7f03f778571264d008.poster.avif?t=1747926077\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/03598419bcf9ff7f03f778571264d008.webm?t=1747926077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/03598419bcf9ff7f03f778571264d008.mp4?t=1747926077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Collect them All!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 different gun types for all play styles: Pistols, Revolvers, Shotguns, SMGs, Assault Rifles, Sniper Rifles, Crossbows, Bladeguns…and perhaps some secrets you’ll just have to discover for yourself…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/4c4c74bd5e6ad34fdc5b7ae9a4e2a8b2.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragr