 src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/c55b6138c63fb4fdcc43f6772b0ae332.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/d9fdf6cc3ce1fa36405df2776b9e5b3a.avif?t=1747926077\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras_big/d9fdf6cc3ce1fa36405df2776b9e5b3a.avif?t=1747926077 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Feel the Power!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run you’ll gain “Tech” points which can be used to purchases upgrades</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our permanent progression system means you get to keep your hard won achievements…even when starting a new run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/55bec765b8e3bb7a00e0154d7718f4ce.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/c961c9cb56280226f87f8b6864510f93.avif?t=1747926077\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras_big/c961c9cb56280226f87f8b6864510f93.avif?t=1747926077 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Lots of Options!</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal - when you’re just starting out. Try, fail, buy some upgrades, dominate your foes and prepare for the mayhem of Hard Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard Mode - when you need a challenge. More enemies, more bullets, more guns!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival - how long can you last against continuous waves of vicious enemies howling for your blood?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075890/extras/19675302db0d87b9d39d7540df52ff0f.webp?t=1747926077\" width=620 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hostile Lands is currently in Early Access.  This means that YOU have a chance to shape the future of the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have lots of ideas to make Hostile Lands a memorable experience…but we can’t do it without you! If you have any suggestions or need to report a bug, please leave a comment in our discussion boards.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’ll do our best to make this the best game possible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
